org.obapanel.jedis.interruptinglocks

Class JedisLock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.obapanel.jedis.interruptinglocks.JedisLock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, IJedisLock

    public class JedisLock
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, IJedisLock
    Class that will perform a lock based on Redis locks It is also closeable to be used in try-with-resources https://redis.io/topics/distlock
